You appear to have left out the vignette. Perhaps you meant:

Katerina takes a long time to set the DVD timer. With the family watching, her sister says You idiot, you're doing it all wrong, can't you work the video? **(d)** Katerina is quite close to her sister and family. **What action would be the most effective for Katerina?**

- Ignore her sister and keep at the task;
- Get her sister to help or to do it;
- Tell her sister she is being mean;
- Never work appliances in front of her sister or family again.
